                <p>With the holiday season fast approaching, now is a great time to pick up a new console for the young gamer in your life. If you're looking for a deal, Sony recently discounted its Fortnite PS5 bundles by $50 for a limited time. There are two options available, including a <a href="https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-Console-1TB-Fortnite-Flowering-5/dp/B0FRSYZGBM" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Fortnite-themed PS5 console</a> bundled with limited-edition Fortnite DLC for $450 (was $500), and a similar package that includes the PS5 Digital Edition and Fortnite DLC for $400 (was $450). These bundle deals are part of Sony's official Black Friday PlayStation deals, and will be available until December 24.</p><div title="6536171 -- PS5 Fortnite Flowering Chaos Console Bundle" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="4963" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6536171 -- PS5 Fortnite Flowering Chaos Console Bundle" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-Console-1TB-Fortnite-Flowering-5/dp/B0FRSYZGBM" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/PlayStation-Console-1TB-Fortnite-Flowering-5\/dp\/B0FRSYZGBM&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-Console-1TB-Fortnite-Flowering-5/dp/B0FRSYZGBM">PS5 Fortnite Flowering Chaos Console Bundle</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-Console-1TB-Fortnite-Flowering-5/dp/B0FRSYZGBM" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/PlayStation-Console-1TB-Fortnite-Flowering-5\/dp\/B0FRSYZGBM&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-Console-1TB-Fortnite-Flowering-5/dp/B0FRSYZGBM">$450 (was $500)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>This PS5 bundle includes a 1TB version of the console with a disc drive, allowing you to both install games from a disc and watch Blu-rays--both 4K UHD and standard--on the machine. The bundled Fortnite DLC includes the following cosmetics and finishers:</p><ul><li>Florin outfit (Lego style included)</li><li>Blossom Backpack Back Bling</li><li>Floral Finisher pickaxe</li><li>Blue Blossom's Wrap</li><li>Petal's Edge Guitar</li><li>Blue Bloom Mic</li><li>Petal Steppers Kicks</li><li>1,000 V-Bucks (in-game currency)</li></ul><p>Additionally, the PS5 console comes with a DualSense controller. This is more advanced than your typical controller, as it features nuanced haptic feedback, Adaptive Triggers, a speaker, and a built-in microphone.</p></div>                      </div><p>Other PS5 consoles are also on sale in PlayStation's Black Friday event, including the limited-edition Ghost of Yotei PS5 Slim bundle. It includes the PS5 Slim console with unique faceplates featuring artwork based on the game, a matching DualSense controller, and a digital copy of Ghost of Tsushima, all for $500 (was $600). PlayStation's 2025 Holiday Sale also includes deals on <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/dualsense-limited-edition-ps5-controllers-on-sale-for-black-friday/1100-6536412/" data-ref-id="1100-6536412">DualSense Wireless Controllers</a>, the <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/playstation-portal-remote-gaming-handheld-gets-nice-black-friday-price-cut/1100-6536433/" data-ref-id="1100-6536433">PlayStation Portal Remote Player</a>, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0DSQSX7FB,B0CMDFSB89,B0DSQWH9BR,B0CMDH9M5W&amp;tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Pulse Explore Earbuds and the Pulse Elite Headset</a>, and a bunch of <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ps5-black-friday-game-deals/1100-6536418/" data-ref-id="1100-6536418">first-party games</a>. The PS5 console deals run through December 24, but the other hardware deals end December 18. Check out all the PlayStation Black Friday deals below.</p><h2 dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0DGY63Z2H,B0FRSYZGBM,B0FRSZT2H5,B0CL61F39H,B0CL5KNB9M,B0FRGTYSL5,B0FRGMYJMG,B0DSLTZ6M3,B0CJT5DJ16,B0C1Q9X8VH,B0DSQQ1P8D,B0BSYFB99D,B0DHY8DC6R,B0DHY92HBL,B0DHY9CZ61,B0CJT9WCRD,B0CJSY6961,B0CJTCQRNL,B0CQKLDWY8,B0CQKL4YTB,B0DSQQ1P8D,B0BSYFB99D,B0DSLTZ6M3,B0CJT5DJ16,B0CQKLS4RP,B0CQKKHT5J,B094WN6SY2,B09RBZ134K,B0FMKQFNFN,B0FPMXPK34,B0FST1H26R,B0CCGYBSW8,B0DSQSX7FB,B0CMDFSB89,B0DSQWH9BR,B0CMDH9M5W,B0FP6H8BRZ,B0FLYKJB68&amp;tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Black Friday PlayStation Hardware Deals</a></h2><ul><li dir="ltr"><strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0DGY63Z2H,B0FRSYZGBM,B0FRSZT2H5,B0CL61F39H,B0CL5KNB9M,B0FRGTYSL5,B0FRGMYJMG,B0FP6H8BRZ,B0FLYKJB68&amp;tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel=